	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tua diligentia arguit me peccati; nam dudum ego accepi descriptionem pugnae <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2653" cert="high">Moscoviticae</placeName> seu <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonicae</placeName> ex <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augusta</placeName> nec communicavi.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Remitto tibi tuam descriptionem et ago gratias.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interea scribitur ad me ecclesias brevi missuras <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l260" cert="high">Cracovia</placeName> legatum ad nos et <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevenses</placeName> propter quaestiones varias <foreign xml:lang="de">(erfröwt mich wol, das mir aber zuͦ werch geschnitten wirt, deren arbeit mir sunst vil ander zuͦbereitend)</foreign> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2653" cert="high">Moscos</placeName> subsidium accepisse a <placeName type="citizen_name">Tartaris</placeName> 30000 equitum et se apparare ad pugnam novam etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Apparere passim in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2472" cert="high">Polonia</placeName> multa et stupenda e coelo prodigia etc.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus misereatur nostri et ipsorum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Coepta sunt comitia <placeName type="auto_name">Badae</placeName>; sed nihildum habeo certi de c[ausa] <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronensi</placeName>; multi male ominantur; utinam res melius cedat quam hactenus.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Söllend wir buͤssen und zuͦ grund gan, sind guͦte mittel darzuͦ.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fastus et superbia [istorum] ascendit in coelum; minarum nullus est finis.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Forte pervenit ad vos <persName ref="p3375" cert="high">Vergerius</persName>; diligenter perquisivit, quid egisset legatus <persName type="auto_name">Philippi</persName> apud <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648" cert="high">Rhetos</placeName>; exposui ipsi rem, qua potui fide.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex ipso audies plura; videtur iam desipere <foreign xml:lang="de">und fast an der kinden statt sin.</foreign></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Redditus est mihi <persName ref="p458" cert="high">Brentii</persName> liber vastus et amarulentus, perplexus et maliciosissime scriptus etc.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Crescunt mea negotia in horas, et vires decrescunt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed ita visum est deo patri meo, qui si mihi adfuerit gratia sua, nihil amplius peto in mundo.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ich bin sunst die 8 tag nitt fast starck gesin, hab gar nüt thuͦn mögend, und hept mich an min schweche fast hinderen an allen minen sachen.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed ita placet domino, placet itaque et mihi etc.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">A <placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Francfordia</placeName> nunquam habui plus ocii; paucae literae, vix 10 aut 12, allatae sunt; propter pestem enim pauci accessere.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed deferbuit illa illic; schola quoque rediit <placeName ref="l210" cert="high">Heydelbergam</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Principes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2498" cert="high">Germani</placeName> ediderunt scripto c[aus]as, cur nolint recipere concilium <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1107" cert="high">Tridentinum</placeName>, Germanice etc.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Posterioribus tuis vera scribis aenigmata; nunquam vidi comitem ab <persName type="auto_name">Helfenstein</persName>, ac profectus est ille <placeName ref="l425" cert="high">Romam</placeName> magno comitatu etc. nec Tigurum venit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale cum omnibus bonis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri 14. aprilis 1564.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te mei omnes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">H[einrychus] B[ullingerus]</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioanni Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae ministro, domino et fratri meo colendo et dilecto.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
